" Marimo vimrc — CodeMirror vim mode subset
" Only supports: imap/nmap/vmap, inoremap/nnoremap/vnoremap, unmap

" === Escape mappings (from better-escape defaults) ===
imap jj <Esc>
imap jk <Esc>

" === Visual line navigation (don't skip wrapped lines) ===
nmap j gj
nmap k gk

" === Yank to end of line (consistent with D and C) ===
nmap Y y$

" === Keep cursor centered when scrolling ===
nmap n nzz
nmap N Nzz

" === Quick save ===
nmap <Space>w :w<CR>
